Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:01:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's to the beginning of our new life{/livelyhood}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but it's still too rash \Nto merge our two lives into one.{/my life is a matter of my personal discretion/is my own business/I will decide myself}{I really don't get what he implies to say, so I tried my best to make it as sensible as it can get, i.e. "it's not 'our' new life, it's yours and mine only when I decide so myself/I have other plans than a 'new life' together"}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.32,0:02:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.59,0:02:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn the yacht around{/back towards the shore}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.83,0:02:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Knight's title requires me \Nto always arrive on time now.{/From now on, I have to be in time for my Knight's battles}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me! \NMe, who you used to love with your whole existence!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.61,0:02:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Between me, who used to console and bolster you, \Nand pachislot...{/I who has many times comforted and strenghtened you, or pachislot} which one is more important?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me. \NAnswer me, Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Because your own parents abandoned you, \Nyou've grown callous to others' affection!{Lit: because your parents dumped you once, you are now prejudiced against accepting/receiving love}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.17,0:02:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so, my love for you is genuine!{she rather says "that's exactly the type of you I love the most" but I don't see that sitting well with the next line}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba Ryo, if there's still \Nany human-loving heart left in you,{/you have at least a bit of human's heart, capable of loving ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,you owe me an answer!\NYou are obliged to answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't rely on me \Nto act{this sounds rather like mawari which is "surroundings/to rotate" and makes much less sense than kawari - "substitude/replacement"} forever as your spiritual{/mental} father.{/I don't fit the role ...}
