Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.81,0:03:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You are disgusted with your father \Nhaving god-knows-how-many mistresses.{a wild guess, since this seems way too personal for daiba to know so he may mean "you have many lovers and abhor your dad"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet you always end up trying to bind people \Nto yourself with father's money.{same as for the prev one - maybe it's that father who is "tieing people up with his money.}
