Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.02,0:16:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Winner - Otonashi Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This marks the beginning of Otonashi Ginya's reign \Nas the 52nd King.{/please be noted, with this aquisition, therefore earns himself the throne of the 52nd king}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This was close...{guess, can't seem to know what's baketa}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.57,0:16:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nail a Big at such a climactic moment{bamen is scene; setting; place (where something happens); scenario; case which I have no idea how to handle}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.61,0:17:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba, you are, well and truly, \Nthe man wielding the Finger of God, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still ages away from surpassing you...{/to even think of something like me surpassing you}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has...{the essense of "think up the rest yourself" - it may be ANYTHING: "it's time [I go]/here is my time[, accept it]/the time [has stopped]" the latter seems more likely due to "wa" aka "has/is"}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo... Wait, Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go away! Stay by my side like this \Na little longer! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go away all by yourself, Ryo! \NLook at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoi, I'm grateful for keeping up \Nwith all my selfish antics{/quirks} for so long.{thank you for accompanying me despite my selfishness}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's my turn to be{/say I'm} selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.02,0:17:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're past the Slothium chapter.{... is over/you're done with ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.02,0:17:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't have to turn away from me. \NLet's keep going together, from now on, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But right now, I want to savor{/taste} \Nthose little last{he says "final/ultimate" but that's supposed to go to "time of extreme joy" and only obliquely imply "the final moments of my life"} moments of my supreme bliss{shifuku may also mean plainclothes, though unlikely, it may mean "in normal human's clothes, no longer as a king"}, alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be my one final selfish antic.
